      <title>OpenAI Whisper 完全指南：高效实现语音识别与字幕生成</title>
      <link>https://kydenul.github.io/posts/9bc9991/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Jan 2026 17:11:59 +0800</pubDate><author>kydenul@gmail.com (kyden)</author>
      <guid>https://kydenul.github.io/posts/9bc9991/</guid>
